result.title: Double click not working
result.content:
Hi Codeforces,

Before downvoting this post, please take a moment to read this.

I'm using Google Chrome (on a Mac). Today, when I tried to look at a submission after locking it during the contest, I tried to double click on a cell, but double clicking didn't work. Similarly, double clicking doesn't work for me while viewing the results of past contests. Can anyone explain the issue? Thanks!

UPD 1: I tried viewing contest standings in incognito mode, and it actually worked! However, non-incognito still doesn't work. Thanks acho163 for his suggestion!

UPD 2: Issue is now resolved. AmrMahmoud suggested that I remove cookies from my browser. It actually worked, thank you very much!
